{
	"nodes":[
		{"id":"537c63440818939a","type":"group","x":-2980,"y":-4200,"width":5940,"height":3980,"label":"Computational Chemistry"},
		{"id":"01066344b3b34b81","type":"text","text":"# Mermaid Map of Methods solving for Electronic Hamiltonian\n```mermaid\ngraph TD\n\n    %% Style Definitions\n\n    classDef operator fill:#f9f,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px;\n\n    classDef math fill:#bbf,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px;\n\n    classDef physical fill:#bfb,stroke:#333,stroke-width:1px;\n\n    %% Core Electronic Hamiltonian\n\n    H_elec[Electronic Hamiltonian Operator] -->|Solved via Quantum Mechanics| SE[Schrödinger Equation]\n\n    %% Branching into the two conceptual layers\n\n    SE --> MeanField[1\\. One-Electron Approximation <br> e.g., Hartree-Fock]\n\n    SE --> Exact[2\\. Many-Electron Reality <br> e.g., Full CI]\n\n  \n\n    %% One-Electron Layer\n\n    MeanField --> Fock[Fock Matrix / One-Electron Hamiltonian]\n\n    Fock -->|Diagonalization| OEigen[Eigen Problem]\n\n    OEigen -->|Eigenvalues| OEnergies[Orbital Energies <br> HOMO, LUMO, etc.]\n\n    OEigen -->|Eigenvectors| OShapes[Molecular Orbitals <br> Spatial Wavefunctions / Shapes]\n\n    %% Many-Electron Layer\n\n    Exact --> HMatrix[Full Hamiltonian Matrix]\n\n    OEnergies & OShapes -->|Combined into| Configurations[Slater Determinants <br> Orbital Configurations]\n\n    Configurations --> HMatrix\n\n    HMatrix -->|Diagonalization| MEigen[Eigen Problem]\n\n    MEigen -->|Eigenvalues| StateE[Total Molecular Energy <br> Ground & Excited States]\n\n    MEigen -->|Eigenvectors| StateWave[Many-Electron Wavefunction <br> State Eigenbasis Mix]\n\n  \n\n    %% Connecting back to Chemistry\n\n    OEnergies --> PhysicalArrangement[ORBITAL ARRANGEMENT & SPECTROSCOPY]\n\n    OShapes --> PhysicalArrangement\n\n    StateWave --> ChemicalBehavior[CHEMICAL REACTIVITY & GEOMETRY]\n\n    StateE --> ChemicalBehavior\n\n  \n\n    %% Applying Classes\n\n    class H_elec,Fock,HMatrix operator;\n\n    class OEigen,MEigen,SE math;\n\n    class OEnergies,OShapes,StateE,StateWave,PhysicalArrangement,ChemicalBehavior physical;\n```\n","x":-780,"y":-4108,"width":1180,"height":1680},
